If a graph [`G`] with [`v`] vertices and [`e`] edges is connected and has [`\renewcommand{\v}{\vtx{above}{}}\newcommand{\lt}{<}v \lt e+1\text{,}`] must it contain a cycle? Prove your answer.

[@ANS(essay_cmp); essay_box(6,76)@]* [@essay_help()@]*

