############################################################
# Solution
############################################################

BEGIN_PGML_SOLUTION
Yes. We will prove the contrapositive. Assume [`G`] does not contain a cycle. Then [`G`] is a tree, so would have [`v = e+1\text{,}`] contrary to stipulation.

